1
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,359
A pig in a sedan chair? You really beat all.

2
00:01:44,879 --> 00:01:46,000
Keep yapping,

3
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:47,879
and I'm going back.

4
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:55,239
Did you take vet meds and turn into Marshal Pigsy?

5
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,640
Even the pig listens to you.

6
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,239
Tell me the truth.

7
00:01:58,719 --> 00:02:00,840
What's your game, taking a pig out of town?

8
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:03,519
This is a divine pig reincarnated.

9
00:02:04,079 --> 00:02:06,159
How could it be slaughtered by mortals?

10
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,200
I intend to take this pig

11
00:02:08,519 --> 00:02:10,079
and release it back into the wild.

12
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,840
Since you're going to see your mother,

13
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:26,639
I think I should come along.

14
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:27,560
"Come along"? Don't push your luck.

15
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,759
We're not married yet. No need to go.

16
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,960
It's out in the middle of nowhere.

17
00:02:32,159 --> 00:02:33,680
I'm worried about your safety.

18
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,199
It's broad daylight.

19
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:38,159
What danger could there be?

20
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,680
It's fine if he accompanies me.

21
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,199
Please go back, Young Master Huo.

22
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:42,759
Lift the chair!

23
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,960
Lift the chair!

24
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:16,280
There's no way you're getting away.

25
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:17,439
Look.

26
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,199
Take what you can, smash the rest!

27
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:25,680
The valuable stuff was moved out long ago.

28
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,960
Is there anything left to take?

29
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:27,479
Brother Scar.

30
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,800
There's nothing left inside.

31
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:32,120
Paying debts is a universal law, isn't it?

32
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,680
Why did he run off again?

33
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:46,960
What is this?

34
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,319
Medicine prescribed for a child.

35
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:53,919
I was wondering what was blinding me.

36
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:56,719
Turns out it's Young Master Huo's sedan chair.

37
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,159
Could you let us through?

38
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,159
Ten gongs beat, and you're at nine of them.

39
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,599
Why is it you again, Fatty?

40
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,120
Young Master Huo.

41
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:07,719
Well...

42
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,759
Little Huo.

43
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:12,240
Even he has to call me Fat Uncle.

44
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:14,159
Move aside.

45
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,560
It's not Young Master Huo?

46
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:27,199
We still have to inspect it.

47
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,319
Line up!

48
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,639
Line up properly!

49
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:40,120
That night...

50
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,399
Scar.

51
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,759
That Scar guy.

52
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,040
Let's go.

53
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:53,240
We searched from that side of the river to this side.

54
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:55,800
You led us on quite a chase, kid.

55
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,160
You're the bandits who robbed the Fan family!

56
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,639
Let's capture them and take them back.

57
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:02,800
Then we can clear Young Master Fan's name.

58
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,560
Blocking us here in broad daylight...

59
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,079
I think you look more like bandits!

60
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:07,240
What do you want?

61
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,839
It's you bunch of cowards.

62
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,759
What are you gonna do?

63
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:12,279
What?

64
00:05:12,639 --> 00:05:13,199
What?

65
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:13,680
Get them!

66
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,920
What? What?

67
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,240
Believe it or not, I'll beat you to death

68
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:52,519
Platoon Leader

69
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,600
Someone is causing trouble over there

70
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,639
They say someone touched a gun

71
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:56,480
What?

72
00:05:56,759 --> 00:05:58,480
Someone dares touch a gun on Commander Qin's turf

73
00:05:59,079 --> 00:05:59,839
Hurry up, you two

74
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,600
Follow me

75
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:02,439
Hurry up, lead the way

76
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,199
Shoot then

77
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:14,439
You think this is still your turf?

78
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:15,480
Shoot then

79
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,680
Shoot me then

80
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,399
I bet you don't dare to shoot

81
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,439
Come on, shoot me

82
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,360
Shoot right here, come on

83
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,600
Shoot!

84
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,000
Come on!

85
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:30,000
Where was that shot? Go check it out

86
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:41,920
Quick, quick, let's go, let's go

87
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,240
Quick, hurry, hurry, hurry

88
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:43,879
Platoon Leader

89
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:44,680
What do we do?

90
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:47,000
Come, come, let's go quickly

91
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,800
Gunshots! Gunshots!

92
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,439
I'm not going, not going, not going

93
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,360
You guys just go

94
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,240
I beg you

95
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,279
Go, go, go

96
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:53,319
Go, go, go, lift the chair

97
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,879
Lift the chair

98
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,639
Stand still

99
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,839
Close the gates! Close the gates!

100
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:02,279
Stop those people for me

101
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:03,560
Come, you come out here

102
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,759
Stop them

103
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,439
Make way, make way, make way

104
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,079
Take our Platoon Leader to check his wound

105
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:15,680
Hurry up

106
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,439
Hurry up

107
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,920
Young Master Huo's sedan chair

108
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:31,480
Don't get it dirty

109
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,920
I have to return it

110
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,600
The height of this pot

111
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:37,519
determines the temperature of the water

112
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,920
Black tea needs brewing

113
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,399
Green tea needs soaking

114
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,879
As for flower tea...

115
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:46,480
it smells nice

116
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:49,279
but it's not presentable

117
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:52,480
Drink tea, drink tea

118
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,279
Good, good, drink, drink

119
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:59,199
Right now, I have the heart

120
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:01,160
but Xiu Gu has no intention

121
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,000
How is that possible?

122
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,120
Young Master Huo, you're overthinking it

123
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:08,560
Anyone with eyes can see it

124
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:11,920
I also know your good intentions

125
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,319
But this matter of forcing someone

126
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:18,279
is something I, Huo, really cannot do

127
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,439
It's not forcing

128
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,279
Not forcing at all

129
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,480
Since, Uncle Dong

130
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,920
you want to make this marriage happen

131
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:28,680
then you have to stand on my side

132
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,279
Help me add some firewood

133
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:33,439
and bring this pot of water to a boil

134
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:37,399
That is for sure

135
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,200
You don't need to say it

136
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,519
I definitely stand on your side

137
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:44,759
Once Xiu Gu marries over

138
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:48,279
the rest of your lives, father and daughter

139
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:49,759
will be free of worry

140
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:55,080
As long as Xiu Gu marries me willingly

141
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:58,120
she will always be my First wife

142
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:02,000
First, First, First

143
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:03,840
Uncle Dong

144
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,440
One teapot

145
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,559
must be paired with several cups

146
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,240
We are both men

147
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:12,840
Since you are standing on my side

148
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,639
then you should know

149
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:18,639
how to persuade Xiu Gu, right?

150
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,840
Still didn't get it right

151
00:09:37,559 --> 00:09:38,799
What's the point?

152
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,759
It's just tea, no need to be so fussy

153
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:54,120
It's precisely because we aren't fussy

154
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,480
that we're poor

155
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:57,879
It's not too late for you to learn now

156
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,559
When you enter the Huo family

157
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:02,080
you won't be laughed at

158
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,840
You went to see him again

159
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,200
Stop worrying about my marriage

160
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:08,240
I know what I'm doing

161
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:10,200
Bad luck

162
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,159
Just bad luck

163
00:10:12,639 --> 00:10:13,200
But

164
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,440
it was a close call, but safe

165
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,759
If it weren't for that Woodpecker

166
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:20,000
who was in too much pain and went to the doctor

167
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,440
even if I treated those sedan bearers

168
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,240
to eight meals of bean curd rice

169
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,639
I still wouldn't have gotten you back

170
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:28,279
Tonight

171
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,399
I must send you away tonight

172
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,519
Thank you, Sworn Brother

173
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,320
Tonight at the Hour of the Pig

174
00:10:36,159 --> 00:10:37,480
the signal will be a dog bark

175
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,080
Can't we pick a nicer sound?

176
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,200
What sounds nice then?

177
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,600
Cuckoo, cuckoo

178
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,200
Cuckoo, cuckoo

179
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,120
Tonight at the Hour of the Pig

180
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,200
the signal will be a cuckoo's call

181
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:50,080
I'll get you out of the city

182
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:54,120
You absolutely must not go out

183
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:56,480
How do you know the Huo family is good?

184
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:59,480
His eyes roll, and his belly is full of schemes

185
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,799
I just don't like the look of him

186
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:04,720
Daughter

187
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:10,000
Look at our family

188
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:12,240
and our living conditions

189
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:15,279
what kind of husband do you expect to find?

190
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:18,559
The Huo family business is huge

191
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,200
In this town

192
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:23,159
they are one of the top families

193
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:26,039
The Huos are letting you be the First wife right away

194
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:28,000
You should be thanking the gods

195
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,360
What does that mean?

196
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,759
It doesn't mean anything

197
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,360
Does he want to take concubines too?

198
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:39,679
You'll be the only officially wedded wife

199
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:40,919
Say no more

200
00:11:41,279 --> 00:11:42,360
There is no room for discussion on this

201
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,080
I won't marry him

202
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:45,120
Indeed, there is no discussion

203
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,360
You will marry him whether you like it or not

204
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,519
If you want to marry, you marry him!

205
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,519
I'm not afraid of what people say

206
00:11:49,519 --> 00:11:52,000
about the Dongs selling their daughter to climb the social ladder

207
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,480
I can take it all

208
00:11:54,279 --> 00:11:55,360
This marriage

209
00:11:55,399 --> 00:11:56,679
is set in stone

210
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,039
Bastard

211
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,720
Brother Fan

212
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:17,879
Brother Fan

213
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,600
I helped you before

214
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:22,639
You promised to help me when I'm in trouble

215
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:23,879
Does that still count?

216
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:28,679
Jianghu folks never flake out

217
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:29,519
Then sleep with me

218
00:12:32,759 --> 00:12:33,200
You...

219
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:35,120
That's coming on too strong

220
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,240
Not for real

221
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:38,759
I need you to help me ruin this marriage

222
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:39,879
This...

223
00:12:40,519 --> 00:12:41,639
That might not be right

224
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:43,559
You just said you wouldn't flake out

225
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,200
Young Master Huo...

226
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:49,440
...is incredibly handsome

227
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:51,360
I'm not just saying that

228
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:53,720
Their family is huge and wealthy

229
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,919
If you marry into that family...

230
00:12:54,919 --> 00:12:58,080
It's like falling into a pot of gold

231
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,799
I've never liked him since we were kids

232
00:13:00,279 --> 00:13:02,000
And I don't want anything from him

233
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,039
Then what do you want?

234
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:06,480
I want...

235
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,039
Moonlight and romance

236
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:10,919
A soulmate

237
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,240
I want romance

238
00:13:15,159 --> 00:13:16,480
A love worth dying for

239
00:13:17,759 --> 00:13:18,919
What on earth do you want?

240
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,080
You wouldn't understand

241
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,279
Will you help me or not?

242
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,600
Young Master Huo...

243
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:30,919
...has a pretty good temper

244
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,919
He puts up with you a lot

245
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,279
You two should just give it a try

246
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,960
Maybe if you spend time together...

247
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,480
...it might actually work out

248
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:41,120
I know exactly what kind of person he is

249
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,559
If you don't help me...

250
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:43,519
I'll just have to die

251
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,639
That serious?

252
00:13:50,519 --> 00:13:50,919
Seriously?

253
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:51,600
Seriously

254
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:52,919
Are you sure?

255
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:53,879
I'm sure

256
00:13:54,799 --> 00:13:55,600
Alright then

257
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:09,519
Sadness upon sadness

258
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:13,120
Marriage needs no tears

259
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:16,279
I wish for a heart so true

260
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,799
Together through the gray years

261
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,639
You should be content

262
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,039
Young Master

263
00:14:30,279 --> 00:14:31,519
This is from Xiu Gu

264
00:14:32,399 --> 00:14:33,759
From the Young Mistress

265
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:45,480
Tonight I'm brewing new wine in the attic

266
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:50,799
You blockhead

267
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,559
I told you to shoot, so you shot

268
00:14:52,559 --> 00:14:53,559
Now we're in a fine mess

269
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,080
What about it?

270
00:14:55,799 --> 00:14:57,320
It was you bastard who spouted nonsense first

271
00:14:57,679 --> 00:14:58,840
Dare to do it but won't admit it

272
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,960
You stole the grain, so own up to it

273
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,519
Which eye saw us stealing?

274
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,919
All these eyes of ours saw it

275
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,279
Can you see clearly in the dead of night?

276
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,279
You slipped up

277
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,519
It wasn't you guys

278
00:15:10,519 --> 00:15:11,759
How did you know it was at night?

279
00:15:11,919 --> 00:15:13,480
Nonsense, how could you steal in broad daylight?

280
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,879
Hurry up and hand over the grain

281
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,480
And I'll spare you pussycats' lives

282
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,039
Who needs you to spare us?

283
00:15:20,759 --> 00:15:21,759
If it weren't for these soldiers today

284
00:15:21,759 --> 00:15:22,639
You'd be dead meat

285
00:15:23,039 --> 00:15:24,000
You punk

286
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:24,879
Come here then

287
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:25,879
See if I don't mess you up

288
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,279
Stand back, let me

289
00:15:27,519 --> 00:15:29,480
I haven't even made a move yet, you fools

290
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,240
Come on! Come on!

291
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,840
Come, come, come

292
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:34,360
Come over here! Come over here!

293
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,720
What's the noise? What's the noise?

294
00:15:38,879 --> 00:15:39,720
Come, come

295
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:42,840
Little officer

296
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,759
Is the brother who got shot okay?

297
00:15:45,039 --> 00:15:46,159
Which one of you actually fired the gun?

298
00:15:46,279 --> 00:15:46,919
Him

299
00:15:47,159 --> 00:15:48,559
It's his gun, he fired it

300
00:15:48,919 --> 00:15:50,399
Sir, he told me to shoot

301
00:15:50,399 --> 00:15:50,759
Really, he told me to

302
00:15:50,759 --> 00:15:52,279
What do you mean I told you to shoot?

303
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,559
If I tell you to do something, you just do it?

304
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:54,759
If I told you to call me Daddy, would you?

305
00:15:54,759 --> 00:15:55,799
See that? Bad person

306
00:15:55,799 --> 00:15:56,120
I'm a good person

307
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:56,919
None of you are getting off the hook

308
00:15:56,919 --> 00:15:58,000
All will be treated as bandits

309
00:15:58,679 --> 00:15:59,799
We're done for

310
00:15:59,799 --> 00:16:00,799
Quiet down, all of you

311
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,200
Sir, we're innocent

312
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:03,279
What do you mean "as bandits"?

313
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,559
Sir, Sir

314
00:16:04,559 --> 00:16:07,639
We aren't bandits, I'm not a bandit!

315
00:16:08,039 --> 00:16:09,000
Stop yelling

316
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,440
Stop yelling

317
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,480
What's so bad about being a bandit?

318
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,039
Being a bandit

319
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,559
Might actually save your life

320
00:16:35,919 --> 00:16:37,039
Cuckoo, cuckoo

321
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:40,360
Cuckoo, cuckoo

322
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:43,200
Cuckoo, cuckoo

323
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,279
He's here

324
00:16:57,679 --> 00:16:58,519
Say something

325
00:16:58,679 --> 00:16:59,799
Say what?

326
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,639
Just say anything

327
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:06,720
Your hands

328
00:17:07,320 --> 00:17:09,720
They're shaking from the cold

329
00:17:11,519 --> 00:17:13,640
Let me warm them up for you

330
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:22,519
Cuckoo

331
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:24,799
Cuckoo, cuckoo

332
00:17:25,559 --> 00:17:27,000
Cuckoo, cuckoo

333
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:28,680
What next?

334
00:17:39,759 --> 00:17:40,440
Lie down

335
00:17:41,799 --> 00:17:42,759
Lie down. Okay

336
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,440
I didn't mean for you to lie down

337
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,319
I meant me

338
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:58,920
Come up here

339
00:18:02,359 --> 00:18:04,160
Do we really have to do it like this?

340
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,799
If it's not real, how can we fool him?

341
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,519
You're being so ruthless

342
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:09,240
If I were him

343
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:11,759
I'd die of anger

344
00:18:11,759 --> 00:18:13,279
I want to leave no way out

345
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,559
Come up

346
00:18:19,279 --> 00:18:21,599
I'm coming up

347
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:33,920
You're no good at this

348
00:18:34,279 --> 00:18:35,319
What do you mean I'm no good?

349
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:36,880
Here I come again

350
00:19:10,519 --> 00:19:11,799
Cuckoo, cuckoo.

351
00:19:14,759 --> 00:19:15,599
Cuckoo.

352
00:19:16,559 --> 00:19:17,839
Cuckoo, cuckoo.

353
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:20,359
Commander.

354
00:19:20,559 --> 00:19:22,400
We've searched the entire town.

355
00:19:22,839 --> 00:19:24,160
This guy named Wei...

356
00:19:24,359 --> 00:19:26,160
...has vanished without a trace.

357
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,680
That scoundrel.

358
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,759
If he ends up alone on my turf...

359
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,599
Whether to kill him then bind him...

360
00:19:34,599 --> 00:19:36,440
...or bind him then kill him...

361
00:19:36,599 --> 00:19:39,119
...is not up to him, nor is it up to me.

362
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:42,000
Presenting him to Division Commander Chen...

363
00:19:42,519 --> 00:19:44,680
...would surely be a great merit.

364
00:19:45,079 --> 00:19:47,440
How will Division Commander Chen deal with him?

365
00:19:47,839 --> 00:19:49,319
Will he ally with Wei's forces...

366
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:51,319
...or wipe them out?

367
00:19:51,359 --> 00:19:54,720
It all depends on the Division Commander's mood.

368
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,039
Brother.

369
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,480
I'm sorry.

370
00:19:59,119 --> 00:20:00,079
I'm really sorry.

371
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,400
Last night...

372
00:20:02,039 --> 00:20:03,599
Last night...

373
00:20:03,839 --> 00:20:05,880
I was making cuckoo sounds all night.

374
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:09,519
I was busy all night too.

375
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:12,319
And I totally forgot about your matter.

376
00:20:17,319 --> 00:20:19,960
There was a reason, an emergency.

377
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:21,599
Tonight...

378
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:25,039
I... have a detailed plan.

379
00:20:26,279 --> 00:20:27,279
Even if I die...

380
00:20:28,079 --> 00:20:29,480
...I will get you out of here.

381
00:20:29,759 --> 00:20:31,240
If I don't get out soon...

382
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,559
...I'm afraid I'll die before you do.

383
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:38,200
There won't be a third time.

384
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,000
Pan Jinlian.

385
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,200
In front of my brother and these elders...

386
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,920
...Uncle demands the truth about my brother's death.

387
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,319
If you do not...

388
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:48,880
...I may recognize you as my sister-in-law...

389
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:51,119
...but I fear this...

390
00:20:51,119 --> 00:20:55,440
...will not recognize you.

391
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,279
Good, good, good.

392
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:01,279
Commander Qin's acting has improved again.

393
00:21:01,519 --> 00:21:02,279
You flatter me.

394
00:21:06,759 --> 00:21:08,839
Thanks to Commander Qin this time...

395
00:21:09,039 --> 00:21:10,799
...everything went smoothly for me.

396
00:21:11,279 --> 00:21:12,400
A small token of appreciation.

397
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,759
Commander Qin, you must accept it.

398
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:19,920
I heard you've been back for a few days, kid.

399
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:21,880
And you only come to visit today.

400
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:24,480
I thought your wings had hardened.

401
00:21:25,319 --> 00:21:27,079
Commander Qin, you must be joking.

402
00:21:27,599 --> 00:21:30,519
It was for Division Commander Chen's Fifth Concubine's birthday...

403
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,759
...so I got delayed a bit.

404
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:35,599
The Fifth Concubine said this tea was good.

405
00:21:35,799 --> 00:21:37,559
So I specially prepared...

406
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,519
...an identical portion for Commander Qin.

407
00:21:39,799 --> 00:21:40,720
Please, Commander Qin...

408
00:21:41,079 --> 00:21:42,119
...have a taste.

409
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:45,079
Good.

410
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:48,359
Very thoughtful. Please sit.

411
00:21:49,319 --> 00:21:50,920
I heard your wedding is approaching.

412
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:53,160
The whole town is buzzing about it.

413
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:54,400
Congratulations.

414
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:55,720
Thank you, Commander.

415
00:21:57,039 --> 00:21:57,960
However...

416
00:21:58,319 --> 00:21:59,759
...that marriage of mine...

417
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:02,240
...has run into some trouble recently.

418
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:04,599
My cooked duck...

419
00:22:04,599 --> 00:22:07,599
...is about to be ruined by a fat kid.

420
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,759
What do you mean?

421
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:09,960
Commander Qin.

422
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:11,799
You have such a strong force...

423
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:14,200
...could you just lift a little finger...

424
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:14,960
...and help me...

425
00:22:16,519 --> 00:22:18,039
Some flies or ants...

426
00:22:18,039 --> 00:22:19,400
...are worth my effort?

427
00:22:19,599 --> 00:22:21,240
I didn't want to trouble you, Commander Qin.

428
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:23,200
It's just that my subordinates...

429
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,759
...are a bit heavy-handed.

430
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:26,920
I was afraid they might cause trouble for you, Commander Qin.

431
00:22:27,559 --> 00:22:28,079
Hold on.

432
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,960
Let's get this straight from the start.

433
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:31,519
Handle your own family affairs.

434
00:22:31,759 --> 00:22:33,680
Discipline your own woman.

435
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,200
But there is one condition.

436
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:38,039
Don't let anyone get killed.

437
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:39,200
It's hard to clean up.

438
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,240
Understood, understood.

439
00:22:41,559 --> 00:22:42,839
With these words from Commander Qin...

440
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,400
...I can rest easy.

441
00:22:58,319 --> 00:22:58,839
Don't move.

442
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:01,680
Get down! Get down! Get down!

443
00:23:02,319 --> 00:23:03,039
Don't move.

444
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,319
You catch one of mine,

445
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:06,000
I take ten of yours.

446
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,359
So you are Pockmarked Tiger.

447
00:23:09,559 --> 00:23:11,400
Who are you to call me Pockmarked Tiger?

448
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:13,640
Jailbreak! Jailbreak!

449
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:14,799
Jailbreak! Hurry!

450
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,440
Go! Go, go! Hurry, hurry!

451
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:17,559
Hurry up!

452
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,720
How come there's no one here?

453
00:23:35,559 --> 00:23:36,759
Our Ma Gang...

454
00:23:37,039 --> 00:23:39,279
...never leaves a brother behind.

455
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,359
Get up. Open the door.

456
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:44,480
Get down.

457
00:23:48,839 --> 00:23:49,559
Sister Hua.

458
00:23:49,839 --> 00:23:51,480
I'm out.

459
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:55,400
I see you guys.

460
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,960
I'm back in again.

461
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,200
Come on out.

462
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:10,839
I'm out again.

463
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:15,680
I'm back in again.

464
00:24:18,720 --> 00:24:22,200
Why aren't you coming out? Come on!

465
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,799
What are you popping in and out for?

466
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:30,200
Boss, let's go quickly.

467
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:30,640
All right.

468
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:45,519
Let's go.

469
00:24:46,359 --> 00:24:47,440
I don't want to be a bandit.

470
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:49,759
Move!

471
00:24:49,759 --> 00:24:51,079
I have no ambition to be a bandit.

472
00:24:52,519 --> 00:24:53,519
I said it just now.

473
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,839
You catch one of mine,

474
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,400
I take ten of yours.

475
00:24:56,759 --> 00:24:57,839
Just right.

476
00:24:58,119 --> 00:24:59,160
Take them all back.

477
00:25:00,759 --> 00:25:01,480
I don't want to be a bandit!

478
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,039
Move it!

479
00:25:02,039 --> 00:25:02,720
Hurry up! Move!

480
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:03,400
Slow down, slow down, slow down.

481
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:03,799
Go.

482
00:25:03,799 --> 00:25:04,200
Go.

483
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,880
Go! Everyone go! Everyone go!

484
00:25:08,839 --> 00:25:10,279
What's with you guys?

485
00:25:10,559 --> 00:25:12,119
What are you doing here?

486
00:25:12,119 --> 00:25:12,720
Fetching the bride.

487
00:25:13,039 --> 00:25:15,160
Fetching the bride? Then do it properly.

488
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,559
What are you panicking for?

489
00:25:16,799 --> 00:25:18,200
Our young master can't wait.

490
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,559
Young people these days.

491
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,920
Just love seeking a different kind of thrill.

492
00:25:22,319 --> 00:25:24,200
We're old now. We don't get it.

493
00:25:25,759 --> 00:25:26,119
Let's go.

494
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,119
Dad, I don't want to go.

495
00:25:29,519 --> 00:25:30,160
I don't want to go! Let me go!

496
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:32,400
This marriage is settled.

497
00:25:32,559 --> 00:25:33,559
You, old man...

498
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,240
...just stay home safe and sound...

499
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:36,680
...and enjoy your retirement.

500
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:38,759
Lift the sedan chair!

501
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,640
Lift the sedan chair!

502
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:42,920
Xiu Gu!

503
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,759
You be careful now.

504
00:26:05,119 --> 00:26:05,559
Don't move.

505
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:08,000
Don't shoot.

506
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,400
Cuckoo. Cuckoo.

507
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:13,359
Cuckoo. Cuckoo. Cuckoo. Cuckoo.

508
00:26:15,559 --> 00:26:17,480
Cuckoo. Cuckoo is inside.

509
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:27,200
I didn't expect you to actually get me out.

510
00:26:31,039 --> 00:26:31,559
Comman...

511
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:33,079
Brother.

512
00:26:33,279 --> 00:26:34,599
We've been waiting for a long time.

513
00:26:37,039 --> 00:26:39,319
Your Big Brother is my brother.

514
00:26:42,839 --> 00:26:43,799
Great kindness needs no thanks.

515
00:26:44,519 --> 00:26:45,680
If you face any trouble in the future,

516
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:46,720
just come find me.

517
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:48,720
I won't have any trouble to bring you.

518
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:50,599
Just in case you run into anything in the jianghu...

519
00:26:50,599 --> 00:26:51,319
Brother.

520
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,359
We shouldn't stay here long.

521
00:26:52,519 --> 00:26:54,319
Right. See you in the jianghu.

522
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:55,839
Then as the green hills remain...

523
00:26:56,759 --> 00:26:57,640
...we'll meet again in the jianghu.

524
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,440
Cuckoo, cuckoo.

525
00:27:10,839 --> 00:27:12,079
Cuckoo.

526
00:27:20,759 --> 00:27:22,240
Only because my father

527
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,920
and Dong Jiuguan were old friends,

528
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,559
did I agree to marry you.

529
00:27:30,319 --> 00:27:32,160
How dare you use such means

530
00:27:32,559 --> 00:27:33,799
to humiliate me?

531
00:27:34,759 --> 00:27:37,079
I've known what kind of person you are since childhood.

532
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,000
What kind of person am I?

533
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:41,400
I just want to fulfill my father's dying wish.

534
00:27:41,759 --> 00:27:42,920
I treat you so well.

535
00:27:43,039 --> 00:27:45,559
Why can't you just go along with me?

536
00:27:46,559 --> 00:27:47,519
Dying wish?

537
00:27:48,279 --> 00:27:49,519
Stop pretending.

538
00:27:49,759 --> 00:27:51,319
You've been pretending your whole life.

539
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,480
It's all fake.

540
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:53,839
You're just a hypocritical lowlife.

541
00:27:53,839 --> 00:27:55,039
You make me sick.

542
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,000
Shut up!

543
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:04,880
Acting like this

544
00:28:06,079 --> 00:28:07,240
only proves

545
00:28:07,799 --> 00:28:08,880
that I'm right.

546
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:23,680
Fine.

547
00:28:26,039 --> 00:28:26,920
Then

548
00:28:27,119 --> 00:28:28,400
we'll just drag this out.

549
00:28:29,079 --> 00:28:31,400
Let's see how tough you really are.
